VIRGINIA HOUSE OF DELEGATES, et al., appellants,
v.
Golden BETHUNE-HILL, et al. No. 18-1134. Supreme Court of the United States June 17, 2019. Appeal from the United States District Court for the Eastern District of Virginia dismissed for want of jurisdiction. See Virginia House of Delegates v. Bethune-Hill, 587 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 1945, --- L.E.2d ---- (2019).
